    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and comfort, having been kept in consistent, road-ready condition. The exterior finish still catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use like small stone chips on the lower bumper. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats are firm and supportive with no tears, and all original technology\u2014from the responsive touchscreen to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is a standout. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent brake inspection and oil change already completed. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. We have kept a comprehensive folder of all maintenance receipts to provide the next owner with total peace of mind. It is a solid, well-cared-for example that drives as well as it looks.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
