      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and looks great on the road. It's been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin, I just know you'll love it!",
