    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2008 BMW M3 (E92) powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine. This enthusiast-owned example features a 6-speed manual transmission and the factory M Variable Differential Lock for superior longitudinal traction. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the critical rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction systems perform to spec. The chassis remains taut with original EDC-equipped dampers and a carbon fiber roof to lower the center of gravity. While the Alpine White finish exhibits minor road-derived patina, the powertrain delivers a linear 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
